Architecture Summary — Flamestreet

Frontend (Web)
- Framework: React (Vite)
- Language: JavaScript (ESM)
- Routing: react-router-dom
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- State Management: Zustand
- Data Fetching: @tanstack/react-query + Axios
- Realtime Client: laravel-echo + pusher-js (Pusher-compatible)
- Rich Text: TipTap

Backend (API)
- Framework: Laravel 13 (PHP 8.3)
- API Type: HTTP JSON API (REST-style / REST-ish)
- Authentication: Laravel Sanctum Personal Access Token (Bearer token)
- Authorization (RBAC): spatie/laravel-permission (roles/permissions)
- Realtime Server: Laravel Reverb (Pusher-compatible)
- Payments: DOKU (Checkout/QRIS/VA/CC) via internal services
- Push Notifications: Firebase (FCM) + Expo Push

Mobile
- Platform: iOS & Android
- Framework: React Native (Expo)
- Language: TypeScript
- State Management: Zustand
- Data Fetching: @tanstack/react-query + Axios
- Realtime Client: laravel-echo + pusher-js (Pusher-compatible)
- Secure Storage: expo-secure-store (token)
- Push Notifications: expo-notifications (Expo Push) + FCM support

Database & Persistence
- Database: MySQL
- ORM / Query Builder: Eloquent ORM + Query Builder
- Migrations: Laravel Migrations
- Sessions: database (SESSION_DRIVER=database)
- Queues: database (QUEUE_CONNECTION=database)
- Cache: database (CACHE_STORE=database)
- Redis: tersedia/terkonfigurasi, namun default app saat ini memakai database cache store (Redis bisa dipakai jika diubah ke CACHE_STORE=redis)

Storage & Files
- Laravel Filesystem Disk: local (FILESYSTEM_DISK=local)
- Upload lokasi utama: backend/public/uploads/... (publicly served)
- Storage internal: backend/storage/app (private/public)

Infrastructure (Current Repo/Env)
- Operating System: Linux (server)
- Web Server: Nginx
- PHP Runtime: PHP-FPM (php8.3-fpm)
- SSL/TLS: HTTPS terminates at Nginx

Environments
- Local: aktif (APP_ENV=local)
- Production: disupport (konfigurasi env-driven), detail deployment belum terdokumentasi di repo

CI/CD
- GitHub: repository hosting
- Workflows: belum ada GitHub Actions workflow yang terdeteksi di repo (deployment cenderung manual / di luar repo)

Monitoring & Security
- Logging:
  - Backend: Laravel logging (LOG_CHANNEL=stack, LOG_STACK=single)
  - Mail: default log driver (MAIL_MAILER=log)
- Error Tracking: belum ada integrasi (mis. Sentry) yang terdeteksi
- Monitoring: belum ada tool monitoring yang terdeteksi
- Backup: belum terdokumentasi di repo
- Access Control:
  - Backend: Sanctum + middleware role/permission (Spatie)
  - Frontend: route guard berbasis token + role

Third-Party Integrations
- Payment: DOKU
- Push Notifications: Firebase FCM + Expo Push
- Realtime: Laravel Reverb (Pusher protocol) + Pusher-compatible clients
- Email: belum ada provider aktif (mailer masih log)
- SMS / WhatsApp: flow WhatsApp via deep-link (prefilled message), bukan provider SMS gateway
- Analytics: belum ada yang terdeteksi
- File Storage (External): belum ada (pakai local disk)

Notes / Gaps (Belum Terjawab Sepenuhnya)
- Hosting/Cloud provider produksi (VPS/Cloud tertentu) belum terdokumentasi di repo
- Strategi backup (DB + uploads) belum terdokumentasi
- Monitoring, alerting, error tracking belum terdokumentasi/terpasang
